  "detailed_description": "<h1>Note</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is developed by one person, so there may be bugs and shortcomings.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world that was once thriving with life, a catastrophic and unknown event has brought the end of civilization. The majority of human populations have been wiped out, and the aftermath is a barren wasteland that is now home to all sorts of dangers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as one of the few survivors left in this world. As you travel through the ruins of cities and settlements, you will encounter various dangers such as unpredictable weather, hostile creatures, bandits and other factions who will do everything possible to ensure their own survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES POLYGEDDON:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer and Singleplayer </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Protect yourself from dangers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/18a8dfb61b9085c48fc9fd73df513857.poster.avif?t=1760542942\" width=614 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/18a8dfb61b9085c48fc9fd73df513857.webm?t=1760542942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/18a8dfb61b9085c48fc9fd73df513857.mp4?t=1760542942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farming </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill system </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests system </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Difficulty change </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transport </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/1244b4c5913315e5439f86388a3f7f81.poster.avif?t=1760542942\" width=614 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/1244b4c5913315e5439f86388a3f7f81.webm?t=1760542942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/1244b4c5913315e5439f86388a3f7f81.mp4?t=1760542942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resource management </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crafting </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Base Building </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >System of health, thirst, hunger, energy, temperature, radiation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open world </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weather effects </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different biomes with their own characteristics </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/b41afee93ac6064c2121793e59b32716.avif?t=1760542942\" width=615 height=210 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character and Weapon customization </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067020/extras/ea157f83f096a094bd8b8f945914f30a.avif?t=1760542942\" width=614 height=154 /></span></p>",
